---
import { Layers, Thermometer, Droplets, FlaskConical, Apple, Leaf, Cherry } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<section id="escalabilidad" class="py-24 bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-200">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">

      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-100/50 border border-emerald-200 text-emerald-700 font-medium text-sm mb-6">
          <Layers class="h-4 w-4" />
          Diseño Modular
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          Crece junto a tus necesidades agrícolas
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Nuestro hardware es modular. Comienza con los sensores básicos y añade nuevas capacidades a medida que tu campo y tus cultivos evolucionan. Compatible con diversas especies.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Sensores Disponibles</h4>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-slate-700 shadow-sm"><Droplets class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-500"/> pH y ORP</span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-slate-700 shadow-sm"><FlaskConical class="h-4 w-4 text-purple-500"/> Conductividad Eléctrica</span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-slate-700 shadow-sm"><Thermometer class="h-4 w-4 text-orange-500"/> Temperatura</span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-slate-700 shadow-sm opacity-60"><Layers class="h-4 w-4 text-slate-400"/> Oxígeno Disuelto (Próximamente)</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-200">
            <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Cultivos Soportados</h4>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-blue-800 font-medium"><Leaf class="h-4 w-4"/> Arándanos</span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-red-50 border border-red-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-red-800 font-medium"><Cherry class="h-4 w-4"/> Cerezos</span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-50 border border-green-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-green-800 font-medium"><Apple class="h-4 w-4"/> Paltos</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
              <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4"><Droplets class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600"/></div>
              <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Módulo Base</h5>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Conexión y batería</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
              <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4"><FlaskConical class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600"/></div>
              <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Sonda Multi</h5>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">pH + CE + Temp</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 pt-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
              <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4"><Leaf class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-600"/></div>
              <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Perfil Arándano</h5>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Algoritmos dedicados</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 aspect-square flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center border-dashed border-2 bg-slate-50/50">
              <div class="h-12 w-12 bg-slate-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-slate-400 font-bold text-xl">+</div>
              <h5 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Módulos Extra</h5>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">Expansión futura</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
